2026-05-16T23:49:49.5511422Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T23:49:49.5512234Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T23:49:49.5512932Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T23:49:49.5544013Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T23:49:49.5544849Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T23:49:49.5545624Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T23:49:49.5546356Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T23:49:49.5547343Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
